text: Janakpuri is a suburb in the Southwest Delhi district of Delhi, India. Janakpuri may also refer to: * Janakpuri West metro station, an interchange station between the Blue Line and Magenta Line of the Delhi Metro * Janakpuri (Delhi Assembly constituency), one of the 70 Vidhan Sabha constituencies of the National Capital Territory in northern India * Janakpuri East metro station, located on the Blue Line of the Delhi Metro ==See also == * Janakpur (disambiguation)
title: Janakpuri (disambiguation)
